reviewText: Not well produced. Periodically there's a voice over saying the production co.'s name. Just cheesy. We get it Nick, you're protecting your stuff..I bought it, so, quit trippin'. I gave it away. Try harder.

I really liked this DVD. She did a lot of interviews for this DVD. This separates it from the other two Nicki DVDs, Nicki Minaj - The Nicki Manaj Story: Unauthorized and Minaj, Nicki - The Lost Footage: Unauthorized. She did no exlcusive interviews for those. It was really interesting.

I bought this video as a gift. i thought maybe there would be music videos maybe concerts. you pretty much have to catch a glimpse of either in here. its just talking and her lip singing to her songs. clips here, clips there. maybe 2 minutes or so. not like a documentary on tv. it doesnt even talk about her life growing up or career. It doesnt have anything to do with "romans revenge" except for the song list they play through out the dvd.
For anyone even close to obsessed with this woman as I am, should purchase this DVD. Well worth the money.
